  "description": "<i>Ichidant-R</i> is the second game in the <i>Puzzle &amp; Action</i> series, and the sequel to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/puzzle-action-tant-r\">Tant-R</a>. Twenty new minigames are present, including rocketship assembly, a batting contest, and hitting the brakes on a speeding car.<br><br>The game once again includes an arcade mode for one or two players. This time, the player is questing to rescue a kidnapped princess from an evil knight. There is also a quest mode which plays like a simple RPG, where battles are fought via minigames. Of course, the four-player competition and free modes also make a return, rounding out the package.",
